<plot>Works in Progress is a poignant, G-rated, romantic comedy feature film that follows the lives of two recent small-town college fine art graduates and a successful, yet unfulfilled insurance professional during a magical summer in "the big city." Works in Progress is set in the present day (with brief flashbacks) in rural western Kansas and Kansas City, Missouri.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?660854</url></doc>
